 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Firm                         profits per         Gross     number of
                                 partner          fees       lawyers
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
1  Slaughter and May      Pounds 377,000   Pounds 113m         542
2  Linklaters &amp; Paines    Pounds 349,000   Pounds 144m         692
3  Allen &amp; Overy          Pounds 344,000   Pounds  94m         519
4  Lovell White Durrant   Pounds 321,000   Pounds 111m         599
5  Herbert Smith          Pounds 312,000   Pounds  89m         448
6  S J Berwin &amp; Co        Pounds 302,000   Pounds  27m         151
7  Freshfields            Pounds 293,000   Pounds 115m         556
8  Macfarlanes            Pounds 291,000   Pounds  26m         175
9  Simmons &amp; Simmons      Pounds 281,000   Pounds  84m         444
10 Clifford Chance        Pounds 278,000   Pounds 232m       1,122
